message: Included more about Nadya's early life, education, and career that are publicly documented but weren't previously included here.

It doesn't seem relevant what other activists claimed about her, when there is little evidence to confirm such claims. I do not know Nadya nor have I ever met her, but I have seen evidence that refutes many of these claims.
This is false, she left PERIOD in January, well before any such accusations.
I do not know Nadya Okamoto, but have run a company for many years that works with her organization, and I have seen material evidence proving these claims false.
